    <content><![CDATA[<h5 id="Today-word-North-South-East-West"><a href="#Today-word-North-South-East-West" class="headerlink" title="Today word: North South East West"></a>Today word: North South East West</h5><ul>
<li>Which(引导疑问可询问去向) Which direction is it?</li>
<li>Block(两位置之间的一部分) Go south for two blocks,and turn left.<a id="more"></a>

</li>
</ul>
<p>1.ABC Industries.How can I help you?<br>2.What’s your address,please?<br>3.Where’s your office,please?<br>4.How do I get to your office,please?<br>5.Where are you now?<br>6.How long does it take?<br>7.I have a meeting at your company today.<br>8.In my car,on the corner of Oack and Grant.<br>9.Drive west on Grant,and turn left on Third.</p>
<hr>
<h5 id="英语学习规则"><a href="#英语学习规则" class="headerlink" title="英语学习规则"></a>英语学习规则</h5><p>不带入中文思考，以句子为单位学习，直接联系英文情境，以一个句子进行发散关联其它句子进行学习。<br>听说读写，听英文想场景（不能看英文），看英文想场景（阅，不能在脑子里读出来），读英文想场景（不能看英文），想场景写句子</p>
]]></content>
